ays\n\n**8 new wiki pages created:**\n\n1. **skill-overlays.md** -- LLM-generated project-specific context files (Carl Trieloff's team). Concept from Apr 2026, already showing accuracy gains.\n   - Cross-linked with: evaluator-super-agent.md, agent-eval-harness.md, my-cursor-claw.md, ai-sdlc-pipeline.md\n   - Category: Tools & Skills\n\n2. **andy-evan-2026-06-22.md** -- 1:1 review: eval scores improved 11→19, flagging system, Prototype Creator integration cost strategy ($25-30/run)\n   - Cross-linked with: evaluator-super-agent.md, prototype-creator.md, ux-quality-rubric.md, andy-evan-eval-review-2026-06-16.md\n   - Category: Meetings\n\n3. **standup-2026-06-22.md** -- Sprint capacity adjustments, customer engagement strategy, Archie CLI update\n   - Cross-linked with: prototype-creator.md, outcome-tiger-team.md, evaluator-super-agent.md\n   - Category: Standups (new)\n\n4. **zack-evan-2026-06-24.md** -- Jira standardization, story points (Fibonacci), skill architecture (11M token context limit hit)\n   - Cross-linked with: prototype-creator.md, evaluator-super-agent.md, ai-sdlc-pipeline.md, rfe-creator.md\n   - Category: Meetings\n\n5. **ai-first-sync-2026-06-25.md** -- Evan's prototype evaluator presentation to full team, 3.6 branch, readiness check concept\n   - Cross-linked with: evaluator-super-agent.md, prototype-creator.md, andy-evan-2026-06-22.md, ansible-ai-helpers-strategy.md\n   - Category: Meetings\n\n6. **rh-ai-first-ux-2026-06-25.md** -- Outcome Creator JTBD integration, QE transition, testing fragmentation, unified testing proposal\n   - Cross-linked with: outcome-tiger-team.md, evaluator-super-agent.md, ai-sdlc-pipeline.md, prototype-creator.md, nielsens-heuristics.md\n   - Category: Meetings\n\n7. **standup-2026-06-29.md** -- Usability testing RFC approved, UX debt prioritization for 3.5, research tooling updates\n   - Cross-linked with: evaluator-super-agent.md, nielsens-heuristics.md, prototype-creator.md\n   - Category: Standups\n\n8. **wg-uxd-ef